---
const {name} = Astro.props;
---

<div class="relative overflow-clip h-xl flex">
    <div class="absolute max-w-4xl max-h-4xl left-35vw">
        <img class="object-scale-down" src="./playcover.png">
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-row align-mid self-end drop-shadow-md">
        <div class="flex flex-col transition duration-300 hover:ease-in-out bg-stone-900 hover:bg-gradient-to-br from-stone-800 to-stone-900 text-white rounded-xl m-20 p-10 drop-shadow-md hover:drop-shadow-xl hover:scale-105">
            <h2 class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-500 to-fuchsia-500 font-bold text-3xl text-left">PlayCover</h2>
            <p>A macOS app that allows you to run iOS apps and games through Mac Catalyst. PlayCover also extends Catalyst with additional features such as device ID spoofing, keymapping, and resolution control.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-[100%]" />
    </div>
</div>